I LOVE THIS GAME. But some of the bugs in the games drives me crazy:
1. The compass minigame cannot be controlled properly. I even have to use a touchscreen to rotate it properly;
2. The 8-bit games are a bit long and cannot control them using keyboard;
3. In one level, I didn't even collect all puzzle pieces, then it still let me pass the level;
4. the game does not support HiDPI.
